title: FRUIT PACKAGING font ID
content:
Hey if anyone could help me with IDing the heavy slab on this packaging, I would appreciate it. The colored type which reads "QUNICE" etc. I cant find a heavy slab that has a Q with a tail like that and includes condensed or compressed weights as shown on a few of the jars.

Thank you so much for any help.

Thanks so much between the two of those I can make this work.
